" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 635px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Algorithm for the diagnostic evaluation of a patient with sideroblastic anemia",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 615px; height: 639px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The mean corpuscular volume is most accurate before the patient has received any transfusion. Mutation analysis where the causative gene is known provides definitive diagnosis and facilitates detection of affected or gene carrier relatives.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
